response.overview: This event took place on June 16th, 2024 at the Nagoya International Conference Hall in Nagoya, Japan. Matches featured • CHIAKI & Misa Matsui vs. Myla Grace & Zayda Steel • Chika Goto vs. Victoria Yuzuki vs. Komomo Minami • Nao Ishikawa & Natsumi Showzuki vs. Kouki Amarei & Utami Hayashishita • Sareee vs. Mai Sakurai • Marigold United National Title Tournament First Round Match: Nagisa Nozaki vs. Bozilla • Marigold United National Title Tournament First Round Match: Miku Aono vs. MIRAI. The event was promoted by the Dream Star Fighting Marigold wrestling organization.
response.title: Marigold Grand Opening Wars 2024 • Tag 6
